Felicity Huffman captured a touching moment of father-daughter bonding when her teen needed a break from preparing for exams. Huffman and her husband William H. Macy have two daughters Sofia, 17, and Georgia, 16. Exam season can be a time of high stress for teens, so Macy was only too happy to do what he could to ease the pressure on his daughter. "Sometimes it's finals week and a girl just needs a nap in her Dad's arms," wrote Huffman. "Sometimes a Dad needs a nap and gets a slice of heaven instead." The photo resonated with parents on Twitter, who loved this example of teens never being too old for a dad hug: